```

```
X = 0
Y = 24
```

---

### Second Line

```cpp
u8g2.setCursor(0,50);
```

```
X = 0
Y = 50
```

---

# рЯУЭ print()

```cpp
u8g2.print("Huseyin");
```

Writes the text **"Huseyin"** into the display buffer.

```cpp
u8g2.print("ERDEM");
```

Writes **"ERDEM"** on the second line.

---

# рЯУ§ sendBuffer()

```cpp
u8g2.sendBuffer();
```

Transfers everything stored in the buffer to the OLED display.

### Display Update Process

```text
clearBuffer()

      вЖУ

Draw Text

      вЖУ

sendBuffer()

      вЖУ

OLED Display Updated
```

Using a buffer prevents visible screen flickering.

---

# вП≥ delay()

```cpp
